{"tid":799582,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"XPS 13 9360 經常斷線死機","createTime":"2018-08-30T07:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T15:54:14.000Z","uid":146728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf122a5e7cc514744dd603d8a014b4f2e807328","tid":799582,"uid":146728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"我部xps 13 9360 (7代U)<br />\n最近一個月wifi經常斷線，起初以為係更新左windows後既一啲Bug. 咁大概一晚最多三次到<br />\n但每次斷線，你唔會load到search Wi-Fi 個果版面。只會不斷空白不斷load. 呢段期間我肯定屋企wifi係正常，電話可以用到wifi,唯獨部xps 13上唔到網。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/150429_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F150429_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a72d91fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/150422_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F150422_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=691cba55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我上網search過，xps13 張killer 1535 Wi-Fi card 係有用家話會斷線，但啲post都係一年前既，最近都無人再討論<br />\n<br />\n我係到諗，唔通張wifi card 係問題主因? 跟著我繼續深究落去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/150934_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F150934_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=00e6c1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自動debug無反應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/151002_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F151002_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1d085007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工作管理員寫cpu 100%<br />\n<br />\n係呢到我開始諗，究竟問題主因係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/151115_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F151115_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0ed7dbb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n連我想熄左個工作管理員，都會hang機。吊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/151204_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F151204_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8ecdd4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後唯有諗著從新開機，但竟然連reboot 都無反應，淨係黑mon，但仲有電<br />\n<br />\n最後只能夠禁實粒power制強行熄機<br />\n<br />\n熄完機再開番又會好似無事發生過咁，又上得返網<br />\n<br />\n原本呢個問題都係斷斷續續發生，但我岩岩由開機到開youtube聽歌，聽左唔夠1分鐘就斷線。從新開機唔夠兩分鐘又一次再斷，<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟有無巴打知唔知問題出左係邊?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e7c0b5abdcfbba0522eb9a4baa05611f8054d7","tid":799582,"uid":97439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cf122a5e7cc514744dd603d8a014b4f2e807328","tid":799582,"uid":146728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"我部xps 13 9360 (7代U)<br />\n最近一個月wifi經常斷線，起初以為係更新左windows後既一啲Bug. 咁大概一晚最多三次到<br />\n但每次斷線，你唔會load到search Wi-Fi 個果版面。只會不斷空白不斷load. 呢段期間我肯定屋企wifi係正常，電話可以用到wifi,唯獨部xps 13上唔到網。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/150429_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F150429_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a72d91fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img sr